block

Very easy to control:

• <b>→, k, Space, Enter, Page Down<r> – Next slide
• <b>←, j, Backspace, Page Up<r> – Previous slide
• <b>↑, Home<r> – First slide
• <b>↓, End<r> – Last slide
• <b>b<r> – Blank / restore screen
• <b>s<r> – Show / hide status line
• <b>r<r> – Reload slides
• <b>p<r> – Export to PDF
• <b>Esc, q<r> – Quit
